OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FCrime statistics have fallen by almost
OL,7,F10% in Gillingham town centre
OL,8,Ffollowing an increase in police
OL,9,Fpatrols.
OL,11,FKent Police say it's resulted in
OL,12,Freductions in burglaries, thefts and
OL,13,Fsexual offences in the area.
OL,15,FResponding to concerns raised by
OL,16,Fresidents and local business owners,
OL,17,Fthe force assigned additional
OL,18,Fresources in the High Street and
OL,19,Fsurrounding areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
