PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FStatistics show there's been a 9.4 per
OL,7,Fcent reduction in all crime reported
OL,8,Fbetween January and March 2026. That's
OL,9,F74 fewer crimes compared to the same
OL,10,Fperiod in 2025.
OL,12,FThere were also 13 fewer reports of
OL,13,Fsexual offences over that period, a
OL,14,Freduction of 38%.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FAn operation to combat sexual offences
OL,7,Fand violence against women and girls
OL,8,Fis Project Vigilant, which sees
OL,9,Fofficers conducting patrols in the
OL,10,Ftown centre to identify potentially
OL,11,Fvulnerable people and to question
OL,12,Fpeople who are alone and acting
OL,13,Fsuspiciously.
OL,15,FPolice say, as well as providing
OL,16,Fgreater visibility and faster
OL,17,Fresponses to crimes happening near the
OL,18,Ftown centre, officers also have the
OL,19,Fopportunity to give crime prevention
OL,20,Fadvice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FBurglary from businesses and community
OL,7,Fbuildings nearly halved, from 11
OL,8,Freports between January and March 2025
OL,9,Fto six in the same period this year.
OL,11,FMotor vehicle thefts also decreased by
OL,12,F37%, from 16 to 11 incidents, and
OL,13,Ftheft from a vehicle dropped by 56% as
OL,14,Freports went from 18 to 8 in the
OL,15,Fcomparative quarter of the year.
OL,17,FThe force said officers have also been
OL,18,Fsuccessful in identifying repeat
OL,19,Fburglars and thieves, bringing them to
OL,20,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
