OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FIn one incident, Kent Police was
OL,7,Fcalled to reports of a theft of a car
OL,8,Fnear the town centre on 28 March 2026.
OL,9,FFollowing an investigation, on 1
OL,10,FApril, a 17 year old was arrested and
OL,11,Fsubsequently charged.
OL,13,FAs part of the ongoing crackdown on
OL,14,Fcrime, an operation was held on Friday
OL,15,F10 April in which officers patrolled
OL,16,Fthe streets, made arrests and provided
OL,17,Fcrime prevention advice to the
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FSix people were detained over the
OL,7,Fcourse of the morning, leading to five
OL,8,Fbeing charged with offences including
OL,9,Fcriminal damage, breaching a Criminal
OL,10,FBehaviour Order, and shoplifting.
OL,12,FWorking in partnership with British
OL,13,FTransport Police, stop and searches
OL,14,Fwere conducted at the town's train
OL,15,Fstation to ensure no drugs or weapons
OL,16,Fwere being brought into the area
OL,17,Fthrough the rail system.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,FMedway Chief Inspector Gary Woodward
OL,7,Fsaid: "Engaging with residents and
OL,8,Fbusiness owners is just one part of
OL,9,Four ongoing efforts to stamp down on
OL,10,Fcrime in Gillingham.
OL,12,F"Our proactivity is evidently having
OL,13,Fan impact, with these excellent
OL,14,Fstatistics showing that criminals are
OL,15,Faware we will find them and bring them
OL,16,Fto justice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776935153
OL,3,CIncreased patrols see crime statistics
OL,4,Cfall almost 10%
OL,6,F"But we also know one crime is one too
OL,7,Fmany and those who live, work and
OL,8,Fvisit Gillingham should know that our
OL,9,Fefforts won't stop just because we've
OL,10,Fseen a noticeable decrease in crime.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank residents for
OL,13,Fengaging with us so that we can
OL,14,Faddress their concerns and ensure the
OL,15,Fcommunity is a safe place for all to
OL,16,Fenjoy.'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
